com.betfair.cougar.client.factory

Class AbstractCougarClientFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.betfair.cougar.client.factory.AbstractCougarClientFactory

  • public abstract class AbstractCougarClientFactory
extends Object
    Base cougar client service factory that registers client services with the specified parameters. Currently works with only synchronous http transport. - Creates a new instance of the transport - Initialises the executable resolver with the transport and the operation keys - Packages the whole thing into a service registration request and introduces the service to EV
